## Locking

This project includes DynamoDB-backed lease-lock helpers.

Terraform provisions the lock table. Correct locking depends on runtime code using conditional writes for:

| Operation | Requirement                                             |
| --------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Acquire   | Lock is absent, expired, or already owned by the caller |
| Heartbeat | Caller still owns the lock                              |
| Release   | Caller still owns the lock                              |

A stale worker must not be able to release or heartbeat a lock acquired by a newer worker.
{% endif %}

